{"data":[{"date":"08:04 25/06","title":"C\u0110V th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi m\u00e0n b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Senegal c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/cdv-thich-thu-voi-man-bay-viet-vi-nua-doi-hinh-senegal-cua-nguoi-nhat.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c theo nh\u00f3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a trong pha Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t. </h2><div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273445/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi m\u00e0n Nh\u1eadt b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Senegal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u0110V th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi m\u00e0n Nh\u1eadt b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Senegal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/0_1.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u1edd m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng run s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal, c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Samurai khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Sadio Mane th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e2ng cao b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u00e0 l\u00e0 6 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng ng\u1ea9n ng\u01a1 khi b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i bi\u00ean c\u0103ng c\u1edd b\u00e1o vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/1_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"B\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\", t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n So Mexican th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/2_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn. 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/3_3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"K\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t pha b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/4_1.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 pha b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\", nickname 3wuor t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/5_1.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/080333-6.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"Ch\u00faa \u01a1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a lo\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi\", m\u1ed9t C\u0110V th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c. </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"550","checkdouble":"189477"},{"date":"08:18 25/06","title":"S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 hy h\u1eefu: Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb thay ra v\u00ec\u2026 h\u1ebft \u00e1o m\u1eb7c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/su-co-hy-huu-sao-tuyen-duc-bi-thay-ra-vi-het-ao-mac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, Sebastian Rudy \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00ec l\u00fd do kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00eam qua, Sebastian Rudy \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Joachim Low ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Sami Khedira. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 25, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh d\u00ednh nguy\u00ean c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p h\u1eadu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p v\u00f4 \u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n khi\u1ebfn Sebastian Rudy ch\u1ea3y m\u00e1u r\u00f2ng r\u00f2ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau khi v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u00fd do tr\u1eddi \u01a1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/180624_141340_109.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0110\u1ee9c, Sebastian Rudy ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Theo lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a FIFA, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u00e1o d\u00ednh m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. BHL \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 HLV Joachim Low c\u0169ng ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd Sebastian Rudy kho\u1ea3ng 5 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng 10 \u0111\u1ea5u 11 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch t\u1ea1i sao Sebastian Rudy l\u1ea1i c\u1edfi tr\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn ra m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 n\u00e9m h\u1ebft \u00e1o \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c, Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eefa th\u1eb9n khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Sebastian Rudy b\u1ecb v\u1ee1 m\u0169i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady c\u1ee7a Sebastian Rudy.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 5 ph\u00fat Sebastian Rudy v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ngay sau khi Gundogan v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, h\u1ecd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. May m\u1eafn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-duc-21-thuy-dien-421-189417.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nguoc-dong-kinh-di-ngay-ve-cua-marco-reus-421-189411.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh d\u1ecb: Ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Marco Reus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil-421-189410.html\">HLV Joachim Low n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Mesut Ozil?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-thuy-dien-day-la-that-bai-cay-dang-nhat-trong-su-nghiep-cam-quan-cua-toi-421-189407.html\">HLV Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\">Trai \u0111\u1eb9p Marco Reus n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-dau-tim-cua-dt-duc-421-189380.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111au tim c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-loew-lai-gay-bao-khi-tai-hien-man-an-ri-mui-421-189386.html\">HLV Joachim Loew l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n \u0103n ... r\u1ec9 m\u0169i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"549","checkdouble":"189479"},{"date":"08:45 25/06","title":"C\u00fa hat-trick l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u00fap Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/cu-hattrick-lich-su-giup-harry-kane-tu-tin-vo-dich-world-cup.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 52 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Tunisia t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i Anh \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Tunisia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Harry-Kane-tu-tin-cung-DT-Anh-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh s\u1ea3n sinh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Harry Kane c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 th\u1ee9 ba trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u1eadp hat-trick \u1edf World Cup sau hai ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Geoff Hurst (1966) v\u00e0 Gary Lineker (1986).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00e1n c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i ngay trong k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi, ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ebf m\u00e0 Harry Kane c\u00e0ng th\u00eam l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Totttenham sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-anh-vs-panama-463-189421.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh 6-1 Panama</span>:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 d\u00f9 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 gi\u1edd s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng Premier League hay Champions League hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o c\u00f9ng Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi World Cup.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u1ec9 t\u1ef1a chung k\u1ebft tranh ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. C\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, v\u1eady n\u00ean trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a nhau th\u00ec ti\u00eau ch\u00ed fair-play l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-dt-anh-co-chien-thang-tung-bung-truoc-panama-o-world-cup-2018-421-189457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/3-ly-do-giup-dt-anh-co-chien-thang-tung-bung-truoc-panama-o-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-dt-anh-co-chien-thang-tung-bung-truoc-panama-o-world-cup-2018-421-189457.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Panama kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 6-1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"548","checkdouble":"189480"},{"date":"08:32 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6): Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-01h00-ngay-266-kho-can-cr7.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>L\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn CR7<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 che m\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1eb3ng sai khi cho r\u1eb1ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u hay h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p. B\u1edfi v\u1edbi CR7, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Fernando Santos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, th\u00eam 1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ma R\u1ed1c, Cris Ronaldo chi\u1ebfm m\u1ecdi ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a anh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ronaldo ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 4 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Santos mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 ngang b\u1eb1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ghi c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-bang-B-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean, Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u00e0ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, anh c\u00e0ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y 2 \u0111\u00e0n em Romelu Lukaku c\u00f9ng Harry Kane \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, \u201cnh\u0103m nhe\u201d danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00e0 Ronaldo khao kh\u00e1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 th\u1eeba \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1eeb to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, thay v\u00ec qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(01h00-ngay-266)-Kho-can-CR7-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nIran c\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (th\u1eafng Ma R\u1ed1c 1-0), \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf v\u1edbi \u0110T Iran t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3, nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn, khi \u0111ang k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1eb7t ra, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Iran ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3. V\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(01h00-ngay-266)-Kho-can-CR7-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Iran c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may m\u1eafn, Iran \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha Carlos Queiroz \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2008, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CR7. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Queiroz t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Sir Alex Ferguson, v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng Iran v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ph\u00e1t huy to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf m\u1ecdi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, khi Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec5n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1eabn nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Ronaldo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7 t\u1ea1i World Cup (n\u0103m 2006) l\u00e0 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Iran, v\u00e0 anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u1eed l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Iran l\u1eadp n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha?\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Preview Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Iran-vs-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B Worlde Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 10/11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 6/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eafng 3/4 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Iran 2-0 trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2006.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-Ronaldo ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 4 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-Iran ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raphael Guerreiro g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ma R\u1ed1c, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, HLV Carlos Queiroz s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Alireza Jahanbakhsh v\u00e0 Roozbeh Cheshmi v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(01h00-ngay-266)-Kho-can-CR7-hinh-anh-5.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 6\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/bang-b.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng B World Cup sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: 0-1</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\">B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ho\u1eb7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Iran gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/fan-cuong-giam-90-kg-trong-6-thang-de-duoc-gap-than-tuong-ronaldo-188-189340.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/fan-cuong-giam-90-kg-trong-6-thang-de-duoc-gap-than-tuong-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/fan-cuong-giam-90-kg-trong-6-thang-de-duoc-gap-than-tuong-ronaldo-188-189340.html\">Fan cu\u1ed3ng gi\u1ea3m\u2026 90 kg trong 6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nMarina Bogomolova ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eef n\u1ed9i tr\u1ee3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 bao ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi c\u00f4 t\u1ef1 quay m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/cristiano-ronaldo-cropped_1f5krpdeo1lzf11ohj93twdos5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\">L\u00fd do h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u d\u00ea</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"547","checkdouble":"189482"},{"date":"08:43 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga (21h ng\u00e0y 25/7): H\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-nga-21h-ngay-257-hai-long-voi-chinh-minh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga \u2013 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch bung s\u1ee9c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhau b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Nga v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u00f9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nhau. Nga b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua, \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Saudi Arabia 5-0 v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp 3-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Uruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p song s\u00e1t Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Jose Gimenez. K\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga (21h ng\u00e0y 257) H\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga (21h ng\u00e0y 257) H\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Nga-(21h-ngay-257)-Hai-long-voi-chinh-minh-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay ch\u01b0a thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018. T\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Samara Arena, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga mu\u1ed1n cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, kh\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Uruguay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. Sau 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1-0, c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a La Celeste s\u1ebd gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng h\u01a1n, ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, Suarez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Uruguay. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, phong th\u00e1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Barcelona c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suarez mo ty so cho Uruguay\" title=\"Suarez m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/chuc-mung-luis-suarez-cuu-sao-mu-tien-the-he-lo-loi-moi-gia-nhap-barca.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Suarez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Suarez suy gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 31. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u00ednh nh\u1ea1y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a El Pistolero n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m cho Uruguay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia, b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Suarez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Uruguay c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1 9 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Uruguay vs Nga\" title=\"Preview Uruguay vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2562018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga 21h ng\u00e0y 25/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Suarez tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i: Trung v\u1ec7 Sergey Ignashevich v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Yuri Zhirkov c\u1ee7a Nga. Ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Uruguay s\u1ebd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu xung quanh khu v\u1ef1c m\u00e0 hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1eafp 39 v\u00e0 35 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef. \u0110\u1ec3 Nga c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef v\u1eefng ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Ignashevich v\u00e0 Zhirkov l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, Jose Gimenez v\u00e0 Diego Godin b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 Fedor Semedov hay Artem Dzyuba \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a hai m\u0169i c\u00f4ng Nga l\u00e0 ng\u00f3n \u0111\u00f2n s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong 2 tr\u1eadn qua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u0103ng k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta cho r\u1eb1ng l\u00e0 logic v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay v\u00e0 Nga c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n g\u00ec, ch\u1ec9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oi nuoc Nga yeu dau cua toi!\" title=\"\u00d4i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i!\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-gau-nga-khong-con-ngu-dong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Nga c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, th\u1ef1c ra c\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng hay nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Uruguay v\u00e0 Nga kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Bung s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nguy c\u01a1 \u201cqu\u00e8 qu\u1eb7t\u201d nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi Uruguay v\u00e0 Nga th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u1ed3 v\u1eadp. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd tr\u1ecdn phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u01a1 h\u1edf v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nUruguay (4-4-2): </strong>1.Muslera - 4.Varela, 2.Gim\u00e9nez, 3.God\u00edn, 22.C\u00e1ceres - 5.S\u00e1nchez, 6.Bentancur, 15.Vecino, 7.Rodr\u00edguez - 9.Su\u00e1rez, 21.Cavani<br>\r\n<strong>Nga (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Akinfeev - 2.Fernandes, 3.Kutepov, 4.Ignashevich, 18.Zhirkov - 11.Zobnin, 8.Gazinskiy - 19.Samedov, 17.Golovin, 6.Cheryshev - 10.Smolov<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: H\u00f2a 0-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Nga\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/DH-Uruguay-vs-Nga-(4-4-2-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Nga tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/co-doi-bong-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-trai-dep-tuyen-nga-421-189263.html\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trai \u0111\u1eb9p tuy\u1ec3n Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-dt-nga-muon-cham-tran-doi-thu-nao-o-vong-knockout-421-189236.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Nga mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-giup-nga-da-bai-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018-421-189081.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Nga \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nga-31-ai-cap-421-189075.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"546","checkdouble":"189485"},{"date":"08:43 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c (1h ng\u00e0y 26/6): \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-tbn-vs-maroc-1h-ngay-266-den-luc-la-roja-bung-no.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c v\u1eabn tin v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00e0nh cho \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>TBN m\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a b\u1edfi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iran 1-0 \u1edf m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazan Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Iran \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mar\u1ed1c v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. H\u1ecd tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Iran \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, kh\u00e9p ch\u1eb7t h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 TBN c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c (1h ng\u00e0y 266) \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c (1h ng\u00e0y 266) \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Nhan-dinh-TBN-vs-Maroc-(1h-ngay-266)-Den-luc-La-Roja-bung-no-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iran 1-0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 54, T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t sau khi Diego Costa t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Iran. Qua \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n song La Roja v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1m n\u1eafm 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c gi\u1edd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu sao, \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal sau khi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap La Roja c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n khi so v\u1edbi c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Jordi Alba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tbn-vs-iran-ton-vinh-bong-da-phong-ngu-421-189122.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/Iran-qua-cam-truoc-TBN-Doi-khi-bong-da-phong-ngu-cung-can-duoc-ton-vinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tbn-vs-iran-ton-vinh-bong-da-phong-ngu-421-189122.html\">Iran qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN: \u0110\u00f4i khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0 \u00e2m TBN vs Iran b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n t\u00f4n vinh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, tinh th\u1ea7n ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n T\u00e2y \u00c1 khi...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCarvajal c\u00f9ng Lucas Vazquez t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc h\u01a1n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i, 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng hai bi\u00ean h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd gi\u00fap TBN c\u00f3 th\u00eam ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Iran. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Diego Costa. 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi sinh t\u1ea1i Brazil b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a La Roja v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac hung h\u00e3n c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN vs Iran Costa an mung\" title=\"TBN vs Iran Costa an mung\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/du-am-iran-01-tbn-ngay-quai-thu-khuat-phuc-chien-binh-ba-tu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Costa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Costa \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. V\u00e0 khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 anh gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u1edfi b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c thi\u1ebfu bi quan. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 Costa \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Fernando Hierro d\u1eabn d\u1eaft lu\u00f4n tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Iran \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9, T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t Mar\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, h\u1ecd t\u1eeb nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Tay Ban Nha vs Maroc\" title=\"Preview T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Tay-Ban-Nha-vs-Maroc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c 1h ng\u00e0y 26/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, Mar\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. T\u00ednh ra, t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Hakim Ziyech c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 28 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a Mar\u1ed1c. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Mar\u1ed1c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u1eafng tay v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kh\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bo dao nha maroc\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e0o nha mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/1529501040692_lc_galleryImage_Morocco_s_defender_Mehdi_.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mar\u1ed1c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c tin l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 La Roja b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo nhi\u1ec1u ch\u00f4ng gai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Mar\u1ed1c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha qu\u00e1 e ng\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Iran t\u1eed th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e2n Kaliningrad s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1eeb Costa c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nTBN (4-3-3): </strong>1.De Gea - 2.Carvajal, 3.Piqu\u00e9, 15.Ramos, 18.Alba - 10.Thiago, 5.Busquets, 6.Iniesta - 22.Isco, 19.Costa, 21.Silva<br>\r\n<strong>Mar\u1ed1c (4-2-3-1):</strong> 12.Munir - 17.Dirar, 5.Benatia, 4.Costa, 2.Hakimi - 14.Boussoufa, 8.Ahmadi - 16.Amrabat, 10.Belhanda, 7.Ziyech - 9.Kaabi<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: TBN th\u1eafng 3-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Tay Ban Nha vs Maroc\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Tay-Ban-Nha-vs-Maroc-(4-3-3-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tbn-ngay-quai-thu-khuat-phuc-chien-binh-ba-tu-421-189121.html\">Iran 0-1 TBN: Ng\u00e0y &ldquo;Qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo; khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c &ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn binh Ba T\u01b0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0 c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/iniesta-thua-nhan-tbn-anh-huong-tam-ly-boi-be-boi-lopetegui-421-189085.html\">Iniesta th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn TBN \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1edfi b\u00ea b\u1ed1i Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-khong-muon-dt-tay-ban-nha-di-vao-vet-xe-do-cua-nguoi-duc-421-188972.html\">HLV Hierro kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"545","checkdouble":"189488"},{"date":"03:17 25/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1edd 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Yerri Mina, Radamel Falcao v\u00e0 Juan Cuadrado, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 \u0111\u1ec3 nhen nh\u00f3m hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ti\u1ec5n Lewandowski v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><em><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh video (B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV)</span></strong></em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\nColombia: Yerry Mina (40'), Falcao (70'), Cuadrado (75')<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBa Lan: Wojciech Szczesny; Michal Pazdan, Jan Bednarek, Lukasz Piszczek;  Maciej Rybus, Bartosz Bereszynski, Grzegorz Krychowiak, Jacek Goralski;  Piotr Zielinski, Robert Lewandowski, Dawid Kownacki <br>\r\nColombia: David Ospina; Davinson Sanchez, Santiago Arias, Johan Mojica,  Yerry Mina; Juan Cuadrado, Abel Aguilar, Juan Quintero, Wilmar Barrios,  James Rodriguez; Radamel Falcao <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"544","checkdouble":"189465"},{"date":"03:53 25/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/lewandowski-1.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia, Ba Lan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2u \u00c1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u00f3p m\u1eb7t 5 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Saudi Arabia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Trung \u0110\u00f4ng thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga (0-5) v\u00e0 Uruguay (0-1).\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhung-doi-tuyen-bi-loai-sau-hai-tran-dau-tien-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>USaudi Arabia b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 4 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n l\u00e0 Iran (th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c h\u00f2a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha), Australia (th\u1eafng Peru), H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia khi\u1ebfn Ba Lan tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ba Lan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thua Senegal v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-2.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lewandowski va Ba Lan la dai dien chau Au dau tien lot nhom nhung doi tuyen bi loai sau hai tran dau tien World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Lewandowski v\u00e0 Ba Lan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/lewandowski-1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lewandowski v\u00e0 Ba Lan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi Nga, Ph\u00e1p, Croatia, Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u00f3i chung v\u1eabn cao h\u01a1n ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eafc - Trung M\u1ef9<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 ba \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c B\u1eafc, Trung M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 Caribe, hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Costa Rica v\u00e0 Panama. Costa Rica thua hai tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi Serbia (0-1) v\u00e0 Brazil (0-2). Panama trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup th\u1eadm ch\u00ed thua th\u1ea3m h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 (0-3) v\u00e0 Anh (1-6).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Panama roi World Cup 2018 sau hai tran thua dam.\" title=\"\u0110T Panama r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/panama-3.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Panama r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 Mexico. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, Mexico ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nam M\u1ef9<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Peru b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn. Peru l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u1edbt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p (c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-1).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot ngay that vong voi dai dien Nam My khi Phap loai Peru khoi World Cup 2018 bang chien thang toi thieu 1-0.\" title=\"M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 khi Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Peru kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/thu-thanh-gallese-khang-dinh-dt-peru-chua-bo-cuoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Peru b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-1.\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 Uruguay. Ba \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m Brazil (h\u00f2a Serbia l\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp), Colombia (th\u1eafng Senegal) v\u00e0 Argentina (th\u1eafng Nigeria) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngang nhau khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2u Phi<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2u Phi l\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng cao nh\u1ea5t. Ba \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp, Ma-r\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Tunisia khi \u0111\u1ec1u thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah Nga 3-1 Ai Cap\" title=\"Salah Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/salah-len-tieng-sau-khi-ai-cap-som-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00e2m v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9. Senegal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Colombia, Nigeria s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Argentina. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Senegal l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7, trong khi Nigeria n\u1ebfu h\u00f2a ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Iceland.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"ar