e=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Them mot chiec ao dac biet cua CDV Colombia.\" title=\"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Colombia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/042806-10.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Colombia.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Net dep cua cac nu CDV Colombia tren khan dai san Kazan.\" title=\"N\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u1eef C\u0110V Colombia tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n Kazan.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/042825-11.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>N\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u1eef C\u0110V Colombia tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n Kazan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chiec mu an tuong cua mot CDV nu Colombia.\" title=\"Chi\u1ebfc m\u0169 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t C\u0110V n\u1eef Colombia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/042840-12.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chi\u1ebfc m\u0169 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t C\u0110V n\u1eef Colombia.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu thanh huyen thoai Rene Higuita ky tang nguoi ham mo truoc tran dau.\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Rene Higuita k\u00fd t\u1eb7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/042915-13.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Rene Higuita k\u00fd t\u1eb7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina ghi ban mo ti so.\" title=\"Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/042929-14.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Radamel Falcao ghi ban nhan doi cach biet cho DT Colombia.\" title=\"Radamel Falcao ghi b\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T Colombia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/041506-982959746.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Radamel Falcao ghi b\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T Colombia.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuadrado va cac dong doi an mung sau khi ghi ban thu ba giup Colombia huy diet Ba Lan.\" title=\"Cuadrado v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 ba gi\u00fap Colombia h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/16.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cuadrado v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 ba gi\u00fap Colombia h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:<br />\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<strong><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-jose-pekerman-khen-colombia-da-dep-465-189469.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan, HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia-421-189468.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-loai-tu-rat-som-hlv-ba-lan-noi-gi-421-189467.html\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm HLV Ba Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-doi-tuyen-bi-loai-sau-hai-tran-dau-tien-world-cup-2018-465-189466.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia-461-189465.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia-421-189461.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br />\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"542","checkdouble":"189467"},{"date":"03:58 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Colombia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3 qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, c\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ba Lan vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba Lan g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBa Lan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E v\u1edbi 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 10 tr\u1eadn. &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 8/10 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ghi trung b\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n 3 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ba Lan vs Colombia - B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ba Lan vs Colombia - B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Nhung-diem-nhan-Ba-Lan-vs-Colombia---Bang-H-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ba Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Colombia, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Senegal, Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cao nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i si\u00eau sao Lewandowski, Ban Lan c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 Szczesny, Lukasz Piszczek hay Grosicki.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ba Lan s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H, song m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ba Lan thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u01a1i \u00e1o 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia. 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t, Lewandowski v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Ba Lan \u1edf World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc, h\u1ecd b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u1eafc qu\u00e1 sai l\u1ea7m trong ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o trung phong Lewandowski khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, HLV Adam Nawalka th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Colombia th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m khi\u1ebfn Colombia th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Nh\u00ecn chung \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong th\u1ebf thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia thap lai co hoi di tiep\" title=\"Colombia th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/colom-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Colombia th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Cuadrado, James Rodriguez hay Falcao, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Colombia t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ba Lan v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Colombia c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng 55%, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 13 l\u1ea7n, 4 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Ba Lan ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 9 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Colombia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-ba-lan-vs-colombia-421-189458.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ba Lan vs Colombia </span>gi\u00fap Falcao v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Senegal l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Colombia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018, HLV Jose Pekerman s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi James Rodriguez, Juan Cuadrado, v\u00e0 Juan Quintero h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 trung phong Radamel Falcao. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pekerman tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac ngoi sao tan cong cua Colombia co mot tran dau an tuong\" title=\"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Colombia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/colombia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Colombia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 4 ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Colombia \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. \u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, James Rodriguez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2, Juan Quintero ch\u1ecdc khe \u0111\u1ec3 Falcao d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa James Rodriguez v\u00e0 Juan Cuadrado. Theo \u0111\u00f3, James ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Cuadrado \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Pekerman tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 gi\u00fap Colombia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan 3-0, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Senegal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 c\u00f4 \u0111\u01a1n c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Lewandowski l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Ba Lan, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot minh Robert Lewandowski khong the giup Ba Lan gianh nhung chien thang\" title=\"M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Robert Lewandowski kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ba Lan gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/lewan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Robert Lewandowski kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ba Lan gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Ba Lan, Lewandowski kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Ch\u01a1i xa khung th\u00e0nh khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u1ea3m \u0111i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Lewandowski b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m qu\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal v\u00e0 Colombia, Lewandowski kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, song vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Thong-so-Ba-Lan.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"541","checkdouble":"189468"},{"date":"04:15 25/06","title":"H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan, HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/hlv-jose-pekerman-khen-colombia-da-dep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p sau khi h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n do m\u1ea5t Carlos Sanchez ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, \u0110T Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tai n\u1ea1n khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ba Lan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Yerry Mina, Radamel Falcao v\u00e0 Cuadrado l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Colombia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/hlv-jose-pekerman-khen-colombia-da-dep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Jose Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ba Lan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Pekerman khen Colombia \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p khi h\u1ea1 Ba Lan \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng. D\u00f9 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e8 n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean vai nh\u01b0ng Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh. Ph\u1ea3i qu\u00ean ngay nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i. Colombia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng&quot;.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u1ee3i khen Radamel Falcao<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Falcao \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ai c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 &quot;m\u00e3nh h\u1ed5&quot; \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Pekerman v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Falcao v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng tin \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Radamel Falcao ghi ban nhan doi cach biet cho DT Colombia.\" title=\"Radamel Falcao ghi b\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T Colombia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/041506-982959746.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Radamel Falcao ghi b\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T Colombia.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Falcao, HLV Pekerman cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Falcao l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m vui l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Colombia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. Falcao h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Falcao s\u1ebd l\u00e0m th\u1ebf \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Colombia \u00edt nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 28/6.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia-421-189468.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-loai-tu-rat-som-hlv-ba-lan-noi-gi-421-189467.html\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm HLV Ba Lan n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-doi-tuyen-bi-loai-sau-hai-tran-dau-tien-world-cup-2018-465-189466.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia-461-189465.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-ba-lan-vs-colombia-463-189436.html\">Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia (KT): Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng, Los Cafeteros s\u1ed1ng d\u1eady hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-ba-lan-vs-colombia-1h00-ngay-256-chung-ket-bang-h-462-189404.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ba Lan vs Colombia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 25/6): Chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng H</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"540","checkdouble":"189469"},{"date":"04:32 25/06","title":"\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh C\u0110V ph\u1ee7 v\u00e0ng s\u00e2n Kazan trong ng\u00e0y Colombia h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/an-tuong-hinh-anh-cdv-phu-vang-san-kazan-trong-ngay-colombia-huy-diet-ba-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; paddi